\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
A 
\emph on
projector 
\emph default
(aka 
\emph on
projection matrix
\emph default
) satisfies 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{P}^{2}=\vec{P}$
\end_inset

.
 They are also said to be 
\emph on
idempotent
\emph default
.
\begin_inset Separator latexpar
\end_inset


